Visualization ranking

Ranking Visualizations of Correlation Using Weber’s Law

This repo contains the experiment data and code from our InfoVis ’14 paper.

Data

The raw data from our experiment and an overall ranking for the visualizations tested is in the data folder.

Analysis

The R files we used to compute statistics and produce figures are in the R folder.

Experiment

The code for reproducing our web-based experiment is in the experiment folder.
